headline: Polen U.S. SMID Company Growth Portfolio Q4 2024 Commentary
summary: During the fourth quarter, U.S. SMID Company Growth Composite Portfolio returned 3.0% gross and 2.7% net of fees, respectively, vs. Russell 2500 Growth Index return of 2.4%.
